lsmod       -information about modules of the core;
lspci       -information about PCI devices;
lspcmcia    -information about PCMCIA devices;
lsusb       -information about USB bus;
lshw        -information about installed hardware;


udevadm
info        -get information from DB;
trigger     -make an event request for the device;
settle      -wait for the end of a process;
control     -manage a demon;
monitor     -watch for the events;
test        -simulate the launch of the event;
